<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Manny & Sons Auto Repair Inc. | Odenton, MD</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Manny & Sons Auto Repair Inc. - Odenton's trusted auto repair shop since [YEAR]. Expert mechanics, fair prices, and guaranteed work. Call (410) 672-5874 for free estimate.">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a3a5f;
            --secondary: #2c5282;
            --accent: #ecc94b;
            --light: #f8fafc;
            --dark: #1e293b;
            --text: #334155;
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.7; }
        header { background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 1.5rem 0; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000; }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
        .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
        .logo-img { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; }
        .nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; }
        .nav-links a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
        .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 1; }
        .hero { background: var(--secondary); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 6rem 2rem; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: var(--accent); color: var(--dark); padding: 0.75rem 2rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; transition: transform 0.2s; }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }
        .services { padding: 4rem 2rem; background: var(--light); }
        .services h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .service-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
        .service-card { background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .service-icon { width: 60px; height: 60px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; }
        .about { padding: 4rem 2rem; background: white; }
        .about-content { display: flex; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
        .about-text { flex: 1; }
        .about-image { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
        .about-image img { width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; }
        .stats { display: flex; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
        .stat { text-align: center; }
        .stat-number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); }
        .stat-label { font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); }
        .contact { padding: 4rem 2rem; background: var(--secondary); color: white; }
        .contact h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .contact-form { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; gap: 1.5rem; }
        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea { padding: 1rem; border: none; border-radius: 6px; width: 100%; font-family: inherit; }
        .contact-form textarea { min-height: 150px; resize: vertical; }
        .contact-form .btn { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
        footer { background: var(--dark); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .about-content { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .stats { flex-wrap: wrap; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-img"><img src="logo.svg" alt="Manny                 <div class="logo-img"><img src="logo.svg" alt="Manny <div class="logo-img">M&S</div> Sons Auto Repair logo" width="50" height="50"></div> Sons Auto Repair logo" width="50" height="50"></div>
                <div>
                    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">Manny & Sons Auto Repair Inc.</h1>
                    <p style="margin: 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 0.9rem;">Odenton, MD • (410) 672-5874</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <nav class="nav">
                <div class="nav-links">
                    <a href="#services">Services</a>
                    <a href="#about">About</a>
                    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
                </div>
                <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Estimate</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Trusted Auto Repair in Odenton, MD</h1>
            <p>Family-owned and operated since [YEAR], providing honest, reliable auto repair services you can count on. From routine maintenance to complex repairs, our ASE-certified technicians treat your vehicle like family.</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Your Free Estimate</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <div class="service-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i></div>
                    <h3>General Auto Repair</h3>
                    <p>From oil changes and brake services to engine diagnostics and transmission work, we handle it all with expertise and care.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-tint-slash"></i></div>
                    <h3>Fluid Services</h3>
                    <p>Coolant flushes, transmission service, power steering, and differential fluid exchanges to keep your vehicle running smoothly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-fire"></i></div>
                    <h3>Electrical Systems</h3>
                    <p>Battery testing, alternator repair, wiring diagnostics, and lighting system repairs using advanced diagnostic equipment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-car-side"></i></div>
                    <h3>Suspension & Steering</h3>
                    <p>Shocks, struts, alignments, ball joints, tie rods, and steering system repairs for a smooth, safe ride.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-wind"></i></div>
                    <h3>Heating & Cooling</h3>
                    <p>AC repair, heater core replacement, radiator service, and climate control system diagnostics and repair.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i></div>
                    <h3>Brake Services</h3>
                    <p>Pad replacement, rotor resurfacing, caliper service, brake fluid flush, and ABS system diagnostics and repair.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h2>About Manny & Sons Auto Repair</h2>
                    <p>Founded in [YEAR] by Manny [Last Name], our family-owned auto repair shop has been serving the Odenton, MD community with integrity and expertise for generations. We believe in transparent communication, fair pricing, and doing the job right the first time.</p>
                    <p>Our ASE-certified technicians continuously train on the latest automotive technologies to ensure we can service both domestic and foreign vehicles with the same level of excellence.</p>
                    <p>We're not just fixing cars—we're building relationships with our neighbors in Odenton, Severn, Hanover, and surrounding Anne Arundel County communities.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300?text=Manny+%26+Sons+Auto+Repair" alt="Manny & Sons Auto Repair Shop">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-number">[YEARS]</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Years Serving Odenton</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-number">[CARS]</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Vehicles Served</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-number">5★</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Average Rating</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready for Reliable Auto Repair?</h2>
            <p>Contact Manny & Sons Auto Repair today for your free, no-obligation estimate. We proudly serve Odenton, MD and surrounding areas including Severn, Hanover, Gambrills, and Crofton.</p>
            <form class="contact-form" id="contactForm">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email Address" required>
                <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required>
                <textarea placeholder="Describe your vehicle's issues or service needs..." required></textarea>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
            </form>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <a href="tel:+14106725874" class="btn" style="background: var(--light); color: var(--dark);">
                    <i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Call Now: (410) 672-5874
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; [YEAR] Manny & Sons Auto Repair Inc. All Rights Reserved.</p>
            <p>Odenton, MD • (410) 672-5874</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Simple form handling (in production, connect to Formspree, Getform, or backend)
        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            alert('Thank you for your message! We\'ll get back to you shortly.');
            this.reset();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
